data.description: Stunning Home on .38 ac Lot!  A two story home with a well proportioned living area. Elegant living room, cozy fireplace, tall ceilings, large window will bring in plenty of natural light with a view to the oversized backyard, with full sprinkler and vinyl fencing in place for privacy. The  beautiful chef's kitchen has it all, including an island, walk in pantry, stainless steel appliances. Main floor you will find a den/bedroom, spacious master suite complete with a walk in closet, dual vanity, separate walk in shower and a relaxing soaker tub. Upstairs  are four bedrooms, and a huge bonus room with a closet. Centrally located near schools, shopping, restaurants and downtown area. You'll have plenty of room for entertaining and summer BBQ.  Come take a look you won't be disappointed.
